    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total beauty. You\u2019d swear this car just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept tucked away in a garage, and it still has that fresh, new-car feel. Not a single scratch or blemish in sight\u2014it's truly in pristine shape and drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019m looking for a new owner who will appreciate just how special this ride is. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to come see it for yourself!",
      "price": 44900.0,
