    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 2005 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This example boasts a factory-spec ZF 6-speed manual transmission and a 3.62:1 limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally impeccable, with the critical rear subframe mounting points inspected and verified. Suspension kinematics remain sharp, retaining factory bushings and dampers for an authentic driving experience. From the high-pressure oil system to the rod bearing clearances, every mechanical metric is within factory tolerances. A true collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
