    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This pristine example represents the pinnacle of its class, maintained with an obsessive attention to detail that borders on the fanatical. The exterior finish retains a showroom-deep luster, free from any road rash, swirl marks, or imperfections, thanks to climate-controlled storage and regular professional ceramic detailing. Inside, the cabin remains a time capsule; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, every electronic component functions with factory precision, and the original scent of quality materials persists. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service portfolio with all preventative maintenance performed ahead of schedule. From the untouched alloy wheels to the spotless undercarriage, this car is a true collector-grade specimen that drives as flawlessly as it looks.",
